# InstaUGC — Cursor Rules
# AI-powered Instagram UGC content generation SaaS
# Read this entire file before writing any code.

## Project Overview
InstaUGC is a B2B SaaS that helps Shopify and DTC brands generate UGC-style
Instagram content (Reels, carousels, hook+demo videos) using AI — without
hiring human creators. Think ReelFarm but for Instagram.

---

## Tech Stack — Never deviate from this

- Framework: Next.js 14 App Router (not Pages Router — never use pages/)
- Language: TypeScript (strict mode — no any types ever)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- Database: Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Storage)
- Auth: Supabase Auth (Google OAuth + email/password)
- AI Text: OpenAI GPT-4o via openai npm package
- AI Video: HeyGen API (REST calls, no SDK)
- AI Images: DALL-E 3 via OpenAI
- Payments: Stripe (subscriptions + webhooks)
- Instagram: Meta Graph API v18+ (REST, no SDK)
- Job Queue: Vercel Cron (vercel.json config)
- Hosting: Vercel
- Package manager: npm (never yarn or pnpm)

