## UI / UX Patterns

### Design system
- Primary color: indigo #4F46E5 (Tailwind: indigo-600)
- Use Tailwind indigo scale for primary actions.
- Text: gray-900 (primary), gray-600 (secondary), gray-400 (tertiary).
- Success: green-600, Warning: amber-600, Error: red-600.
- Border radius: rounded-lg for cards, rounded-md for inputs/buttons.
- Shadows: shadow-sm for cards only.

### Loading states
- Always show loading state on async actions — disable button + show spinner.
- Use skeleton loaders for content that hasn't loaded yet.
- Never show a blank screen while loading.

### Error states
- Always show user-friendly error messages — never show raw error text.
- Use sonner toast for transient errors (network, API failures).
- Use inline error text for form validation errors.

### Empty states
- Every list/grid page needs an empty state component.
- Empty state: icon + title + description + CTA button.

### Toast notifications (sonner)
- Success: green, 4 seconds
- Error: red, 6 seconds, with retry action where applicable
- Info: blue, 4 seconds
- Warning: amber, 5 seconds

